This paper is primarily focused on Automatic Speech Recognition (ASR) using deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses distributed training techniques for deep neural networks, which is a common topic in Machine Learning (cs.LG) and High Performance Computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper involves experiments to study the convergence, speedup, and recognition performance, which is related to Statistical Learning (cs.SD) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
